OL,3,CDriver 'took 20 lines of cocaine'
OL,4,Cbefore killing three-year-old girl
OL,6,FA van driver took "at least 20 lines
OL,7,Fof cocaine" in the hours before he hit
OL,8,Fa tram and then collided with a three-
OL,9,Fyear-old girl on a pavement, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FLouisa Palmisano, known as Lulu, died
OL,13,Fin hospital from her injuries after
OL,14,Fshe was struck on Booth Street while
OL,15,Fholding hands with her parents on a
OL,16,Ffamily visit to Manchester on 22
OL,17,FFebruary 2025.
OL,19,FRawal Rehman pleaded guilty to causing
OL,20,Fher death by dangerous driving in his
OL,21,FMercedes Sprinter van.
