OL,6,FThe 35-year-old, who is from
OL,7,FManchester, left the scene of the
OL,8,Fcollision in Mosley Street in the city
OL,9,Fcentre at about 10am before he was
OL,10,Flater arrested.
OL,12,FProsecutor Rachel Shenton told
OL,13,FManchester Crown Court that Rehman had
OL,14,Fvisited two massage parlours in the
OL,15,Fcity in the early hours of 22 February.
OL,17,FShe added the defendant had taken "at
OL,18,Fleast 20 lines of cocaine" in seven
OL,19,Fhours.
