OL,6,FJudge Alan Conrad KC heard it would be
OL,7,Fthe prosecution case that Rehman's
OL,8,Fdriving was adversely affected by his
OL,9,Fconsumption of controlled drugs.
OL,11,FRehman was remanded in custody until
OL,12,Fsentencing on 27 May 2025.
OL,14,FIn 2017, Rehman was jailed for three
OL,15,Fyears for conspiracy to pervert the
OL,16,Fcourse of justice after he torched a
OL,17,Fcar involved in a fatal hit-and-run
OL,18,Fcollision which killed a 25-year-old
OL,19,Fman in Chorlton, Manchester.
