OL,6,FFollowing the youngster's death, her
OL,7,Ffamily from Burnley, Lancashire, said:
OL,8,F"Louisa (Lulu) was the sweetest,
OL,9,Fkindest, and most generous little girl.
OL,11,F"She was full of creativity and joy,
OL,12,Fand she absolutely loved going to
OL,13,Fnursery every day. Her absence has
OL,14,Fleft a devastating void in our family
OL,15,F` she was our only child, our whole
OL,16,Fworld.
