OL,6,F"We were simply enjoying a happy
OL,7,Ffamily day out in Manchester when this
OL,8,Funimaginable tragedy struck. In an
OL,9,Finstant, our lives were shattered
OL,10,Fbeyond repair.
OL,12,F"The pain of losing her is unbearable,
OL,13,Fand we miss her more than words can
OL,14,Fever express."
OL,16,FAbbie Clarke, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,17,Ffor CPS North West, said: "This was a
OL,18,Fdevastating incident which shocked our
OL,19,Fcommunity, and our thoughts go out to
OL,20,FLulu's family who must bear this
OL,21,Funimaginable loss.
