OL,6,F"Rawal Rehman ignored the stop signs
OL,7,Fand tram warning signs when he drove
OL,8,Fstraight into the path of an oncoming
OL,9,Ftram, and it is clear his driving fell
OL,10,Ffar short of what is expected of a
OL,11,Fcompetent and careful driver.
OL,13,F"Rehman failed to take responsibility
OL,14,Ffor his actions. He fled the scene in
OL,15,Fa taxi and denied that he drove
OL,16,Fdangerously in interview, only
OL,17,Faccepting responsibility on his third
OL,18,Fhearing before the court.
